OL,3,CBehind closed doors at haven for women
OL,4,Cfleeing domestic abuse
OL,6,FThe charity, which is celebrating its
OL,7,F50th anniversary this year, can house
OL,8,Fup to 37 women across the two sites,
OL,9,Fas well as children and pets.
OL,11,FIt also provides one-to-one sessions
OL,12,Fto give women emotional and practical
OL,13,Fsupport after they have fled abuse.
OL,15,FChief executive Hollie Venn told us
OL,16,Fthere is a growing need for the
OL,17,Fcharity's help.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
