OL,3,CBehind closed doors at haven for women
OL,4,Cfleeing domestic abuse
OL,6,FShe said: "We are pretty much always
OL,7,Ffull. We rarely have spaces available
OL,8,Flonger for more than a few days. Us
OL,9,Fbeing established for 50 years, and
OL,10,Fstill being here as a commissioned
OL,11,Fservice I think absolutely
OL,12,Fdemonstrates the demand for the work
OL,13,Fthat we do and actually that increases
OL,14,Fyear on year."
OL,16,FAt the refuge we spoke to a former
OL,17,Fservice user who we are calling Eve to
OL,18,Fprotect her identity.
