OL,3,CBehind closed doors at haven for women
OL,4,Cfleeing domestic abuse
OL,6,FShe spent ten months at the refuge
OL,7,Fafter she escaped a controlling
OL,8,Frelationship and, after a number of
OL,9,Fsuicide attempts, credits the service
OL,10,Fwith saving her life.
OL,12,FDescribing her situation before she
OL,13,Fgot help, Eve said: "It's honestly
OL,14,Flike you don't exist no more. You just
OL,15,Flive, minute by minute. It's like
OL,16,Fyou're in a big black cloud and that
OL,17,Fblack cloud is on your shoulders all
OL,18,Fthe time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
