OL,3,CBehind closed doors at haven for women
OL,4,Cfleeing domestic abuse
OL,6,F"It feels like you cannot breathe. You
OL,7,Ffeel like you're suffocating because
OL,8,Fthere was nothing I could do without
OL,9,Fhis say so, without him saying that's
OL,10,Fok. It eats away at the person that
OL,11,Fyou are."
OL,13,FAfter leaving the refuge earlier this
OL,14,Fyear, Eve now has a house of her own
OL,15,Fand dreads to think what would have
OL,16,Fhappened had she not got the call
OL,17,Fsaying there was a safe place for her
OL,18,Fto go.
