OL,3,CBehind closed doors at haven for women
OL,4,Cfleeing domestic abuse
OL,6,FShe said: "When I got out of the taxi
OL,7,FI was scared of what I was going to
OL,8,Fwalk into. And it's nothing like
OL,9,Fwhat's in your imagination. Your
OL,10,Fimagination is that it's this dark
OL,11,Fgloomy place. And it isn't. It's a
OL,12,Fhome full of caring staff that are
OL,13,Fthere for you the second you walk
OL,14,Fthrough the door.
OL,16,F"If this place didn't exist and these
OL,17,Fwomen that work here didn't exist I'd
OL,18,Fknow hand on heart 100% my kids
OL,19,Fwouldn't have a mum now."
