OL,3,CBehind closed doors at haven for women
OL,4,Cfleeing domestic abuse
OL,6,FWith many councils struggling with
OL,7,Ftheir finances amid rising costs, and
OL,8,Fsome being declared effectively
OL,9,Fbankrupt, there are real fears for the
OL,10,Ffuture of domestic abuse services
OL,11,Facross the country.
OL,13,FAlthough councils have a statutory
OL,14,Fduty to provide safe accommodation for
OL,15,Fsurvivors of domestic abuse, other
OL,16,Fservices are not protected by law and
OL,17,Ffunding pots can often be short-term.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
