OL,3,CBehind closed doors at haven for women
OL,4,Cfleeing domestic abuse
OL,6,FHollie says Sheffield Women's Aid is
OL,7,Fwell-supported by its commissioners at
OL,8,FSheffield City Council, but both are
OL,9,Funder financial pressure.
OL,11,FShe said: "There was specific funding
OL,12,Fmade available for councils for
OL,13,Fdomestic abuse services to administer,
OL,14,Fbut actually I think what councils
OL,15,Fwould say is that maybe hasn't made
OL,16,Fquite the difference that they'd hoped
OL,17,Fbecause there are pressures on other
OL,18,Fbudgets within the council.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
