OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FLevelling Up, Housing & Communities
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our Tackling Domestic Abuse
OL,9,FPlan is investing over #230 million to
OL,10,Fdrive down the prevalence of domestic
OL,11,Fabuse, and since 2021 we have also
OL,12,Fcommitted an additional #507 million
OL,13,Fto help councils provide support
OL,14,Fwithin safe accommodation to victims
OL,15,Fand their children."
